  1251→            session.threadId,
  1252→            `未知命令: \`${cmd}\`\n试试 \`!help\`。可用命令: \`!distill\`, \`!cd\`, \`!filter\`, \`!info\`, \`!model\`, \`!models\`, \`!provider\`, \`!fork\`, \`!abort\`, \`!done\`, \`!start\``,
